      • setTime

        void setTime(Time time)
             throws TimeException,
                    OperationNotSupportedException
        Assigns the time for read information of the right source. The difference with setTime(SerialInfo time) is that this method selects the time from the source that has been selected previously. This is because Time variable only has time information and it has not serial information.
